observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Mayor:
• Municipal Accountant to:
a. reclassify the amount debited to Construction in Progress account to Advances to Contractors totaling ₱2,844,450.00;
• GSO-Designate/Acting Municipal Treasurer to:
a. use and completely fill out the RPCPPE format prescribed under the NGAS Manual (Annex 49);
b. complete physical count of all properties of the Municipality on all funds;
c. use of new chart of accounts prescribed under COA Circular No. 2015-009 on the classification of counted properties;
d. maintain complete property cards and ARE for all PPEs, and;
• Municipal Accountant and GSO Designate/Acting Municipal Treasurer to:
a. evaluate and work coordinately on all causes of discrepancies towards the reconciliation to ascertain the accuracy of the PPE balances in the financial statements.
We also recommended to the Municipal Mayor that the Budget Officer appropriate funds again in the ensuing year for the filling up of the General Services Officer to have a permanent official who will assume the duties and responsibilities in the office and to address the perennial issues relative to the supply and property management of the Municipality.
